    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont know if i can talk to a stranger about this. it feels so pointless. i just feel like i'm waiting for something that's never coming back. it feels more like i'm just existing instead of living, and i wonder if it's even worth the effort to keep trying to fight it all the time. do you think there's ever a point where it's okay to just... let go?",
